Package: vyos
Type: Package
Title: Interface for Multiple Data Providers EDDS and FRED
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-01-27
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sermet", "Pekin", , "sermetpekin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre" , "cph"))
  )
Maintainer: Sermet Pekin <sermetpekin@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/SermetPekin/vyos
BugReports: https://github.com/SermetPekin/vyos/issues
Description: Interface for multiple data sources such as EDDS API of Central Bank of the Republic of TÃ¼rkiye and FRED API of Federal Reserve Bank.
    It provides caching ability with selection of periods in order to increase speed and efficiency of the requests. 
    Combines datasets requested from different sources which helps users by combining when the data has common frequencies. 
    While combining data frame when possible it also keeps all requested data available as separate data frames to increase efficiency.
